<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٣ المقنع مع الشرح الكبير والإنصاف ٥/١٨٣.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٤ <span class="c1">"٤ - ٤"</span> ليست في <span class="c1">"ح"</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٥ في <span class="c1">"ح"</span>: <span class="c1">"الوقت"</span>.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>